<para style="p">

  <verse number="19" style="v" />But I hope in the Lord Jesus to send Timothy to you soon, so that I may also be encouraged when I know the things about you.

  <verse number="20" style="v" />For I have no one else with his same attitude, who is truly anxious for you.

  <verse number="21" style="v" />For they all seek their own interests, not the things of Jesus Christ.
